inabatangan District|Kinabatangan]]\n| 18\n| 9\n| 0\n| 9\n|-\n| 4\n| [[Kota Belud District|Kota Belud]]\n| 5\n| 4\n| 0\n| 1\n|-\n| 5\n| [[Kota Kinabalu District|Kota Kinabalu]]\n| 35\n| 16\n| 1\n| 18\n|-\n| 6\n| [[Kunak District|Kunak]]\n| 8\n| 3\n| 0\n| 5\n|-\n| 7\n| [[Lahad Datu District|Lahad Datu]]\n| 38\n| 27\n| 0\n| 11\n|-\n| 8\n| [[Papar District|Papar]]\n| 4\n| 1\n| 0\n| 3\n|-\n| 9\n| [[Penampang District|Penampang]]\n| 10\n| 0\n| 0\n| 10\n|-\n| 10\n| [[Putatan District|Putatan]]\n| 8\n| 4\n| 0\n| 2\n|-\n| 11\n| [[Ranau District|Ranau]]\n| 2\n| 2\n| 0\n| 0\n|-\n| 12\n| [[Sandakan District|Sandakan]]\n| 20\n| 11\n| 0\n| 9\n|-\n| 13\n| [[Semporna District|Semporna]]\n| 2\n| 0\n| 0\n| 2\n|-\n| 14\n| [[Sipitang District|Sipitang]]\n| 4\n| 4\n| 0\n| 0\n|-\n| 15\n| [[Tambunan District|Tambunan]]\n| 3\n| 0\n| 1\n| 2\n|-\n| 16\n| [[Tawau District|Tawau]]\n| 70\n| 12\n| 1\n| 57\n|-\n| 17\n| [[Tuaran District|Tuaran]]\n| 18\n| 5\n| 0\n| 13\n|-\n! colspan=\"2\"| '''Total'''\n! '''260'''\n! '''103''' \n! '''3'''\n! '''154'''\n|}\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable mw-collapsible mw-collapsed\"\n|+{{nowrap|Details of the confirmed death cases in Sabah}}\n! colspan=\"2\" | Case Number\n!! width=8%|Date of Death\n!! width=8%|Nationality\n!! width=5%|Gender\n!! width=4%|Age\n!! width=17%|Hospitalised Location\n!! width=50%|Patient Data\n!! width=5%|Source\n|-\n| 1\n| 152\n| 20 March 2020\n| {{MYS}}\n| Male\n| 58\n| {{flagicon image|Flag of Sabah.svg}} Tawau Hospital\n| Part of the religious gathering cluster. Hospitalised on 9 March 2020 after showing [[severe acute respiratory infection]] (SARI) symptoms.\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.facebook.com/kementeriankesihatanmalaysia/posts/10156846035326237|title=Ministry of Health of Malaysia|via=Facebook|accessdate=21 March 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2\n| 2200\n| 4 April 2020\n| {{MYS}}\n| Male\n| 66\n| {{flagicon image|Flag of Sabah.svg}} Keningau Hospital\n| Had chronic illness. Hospitalised on 26 March 2020.\n| <ref>{{cite web|url